<div class="hero-mancer chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-egg"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "HEROMANCER.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="{{patreonUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>A rebuilt wizard you can drag, resize, and that remembers where you left off, with live progress tracking and a one-click Randomize.</li>
      <li>Reworked Identity, Abilities, HP, Advancements, and Equipment tabs with searchable pickers and live validation.</li>
      <li>Make your advancement choices (ability scores, proficiencies, features) right in the wizard, applied automatically when the character is created.</li>
      <li>A new Equipment tab with a shop, a gold budget, and "take starting wealth instead" options.</li>
      <li>Level-Up mode with multiclassing and a live preview of what you gain.</li>
      <li>Optional GM approval: submit a character for review, and GMs approve or reject it.</li>
      <li>A live character HUD, plus side-by-side Compare and pinning of your options.</li>
      <li>Built-in support for Tokenizer 2, Spell Book, Calendaria, and Dice So Nice.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Changes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>The module is always on once installed; the Enable toggle is gone.</li>
      <li>Alignment and Faith are now plain text fields, and the character-detail pools and Mandatory Fields configurator are replaced by Enforce Biography and Enforce Art toggles.</li>
      <li>The random roll-table biography buttons and the CPR integration have been removed.</li>
      <li>Compendium sources are now managed through D&D5e's Compendium Browser.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "HEROMANCER.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
